ext-text-secondary mt-4\">Thriller, Drama, Survival</p><blockquote class=\"mt-8 pl-4 border-l-2 border-accent\"><p class=\"text-[15px] font-normal text-text-secondary leading-relaxed italic\">“<!-- -->One of the best post-9/11 anxiety films. The ending is devastating in a way that recontextualizes the entire movie.<!-- -->”</p></blockquote><blockquote class=\"mt-4 pl-4 border-l-2 border-accent\"><p class=\"text-[15px] font-normal text-text-secondary leading-relaxed italic\">“<!-- -->Slow and repetitive. The husband is insufferable and the wife deserved better writing.<!-- -->”</p></blockquote></div></section><section class=\"py-24 px-6 bg-surface-secondary\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl mx-auto\"><p class=\"text-[14px] font-normal text-text-secondary mb-8\">Browse by theme</p><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4\"><button class=\"text-left transition-all duration-500 ease-out opacity-0 -translate-x-4\" style=\"transition-delay:100ms\"><span class=\"text-[24px] font-semibold transition-colors text-accent\">All</span></button><button class=\"text-left transition-all duration-500 ease-out opacity-0 -translate-x-4\" style=\"transition-delay:160ms\"><span class=\"relative inline-block\"><span class=\"text-[24px] font-semibold transition-colors text-text-primary hover:text-accent\">Bunker</span></span></button><button class=\"text-left transition-all duration-500 ease-out opacity-0 -translate-x-4\" style=\"transition-delay:240ms\"><span class=\"relative inline-block\"><span class=\"text-[24px] font-semibold transition-colors text-text-primary hover:text-accent\">Claustrophobic</span></span></button><button class=\"text-left transition-all duration-500 ease-out opacity-0 -translate-x-4\" style=\"transition-delay:320ms\"><span class=\"relative inline-block\"><span class=\"text-[24px] font-semibold transition-colors text-text-primary hover:text-accent\">Confined</span></span></button><button class=\"text-left transition-all duration-500 ease-out opacity-0 -translate-x-4\" style=\"tran